@startuml
title AndroidCI Deployment Process - Continuous Integration Pipeline

actor Developer
participant "Jenkins Master\n(2.60.3-alpine)" as Jenkins
participant "Docker Host" as Docker
participant "Docker Container\n(Build Agent)" as Container
participant "Android SDK\nDocker Image" as SDK
participant "Android Project\nRepository" as Repo
database "jenkins_home\n(Volume)" as Volume
participant "Build Artifacts" as Artifacts

Developer -> Jenkins: Trigger Build Job
activate Jenkins

Jenkins -> Volume: Load Configuration\n(Environment Variables)
activate Volume
Volume --> Jenkins: Configuration Loaded
deactivate Volume

Jenkins -> Docker: Request Docker Container\n(via Docker Plugin)
activate Docker

Docker -> SDK: Pull Android SDK Image
activate SDK
SDK --> Docker: Image Ready
deactivate SDK

Docker -> Container: Create & Start Container\n(Build Agent)
activate Container

Docker -> Container: Mount jenkins_home Volume
Docker -> Container: Setup SSH Authentication
Container --> Docker: Container Ready
Docker --> Jenkins: Build Agent Available

Jenkins -> Container: Schedule Build Job
Container -> Repo: Clone/Pull Android Project
activate Repo
Repo --> Container: Source Code Retrieved
deactivate Repo

Container -> Container: Execute Build Steps\n(Gradle Build)
activate Container

Container -> Container: Run Android Lint\n(via Android Lint Plugin)
Container -> Container: Execute Tests
deactivate Container

alt Build Successful
    Container -> Artifacts: Generate Build Artifacts\n(APK, Test Reports)
    activate Artifacts
    Container --> Jenkins: Build Success
    Jenkins -> Artifacts: Store Artifacts
    Artifacts --> Jenkins: Artifacts Stored
    deactivate Artifacts
    Jenkins --> Developer: Build Success Notification
else Build Failed
    Container --> Jenkins: Build Failure
    Jenkins --> Developer: Build Failure Notification
end

Jenkins -> Docker: Cleanup Request
Docker -> Container: Stop & Remove Container
deactivate Container
deactivate Docker

deactivate Jenkins

@enduml
